---
description: Code comments must be written in English only
globs: "**/*.{go,c,h,js,jsx,ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: true
---

# English-only code comments

- All comments in source files (line comments, block comments, godoc) must be **English**.
- Do not use Chinese or other non-English languages in comments.
- Prefer plain ASCII punctuation in comments (`...`, `->`) when practical.
- User-facing docs (`README.md`, `docs/`, `roadmap/`) may use other languages when the project already does; this rule applies to **code comments only**.
